<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About Movies Hub</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, #5d5c61, #379683);
        color: #b1a296;
      }

      header {
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, #557a95, #7395ae);
        color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      nav {
        position: sticky;
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, #567c97, #7395ae);
        color: #fff;
        padding: 10px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
      }

      nav a {
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 10px;
        margin: 0 10px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
      }

      nav a:hover {
        background-color: #5d5c61;
        transform: scale(1.1);
      }

      .logout-btn {
        background-color: #7395ae;
        border: none;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
      }

      .logout-btn:hover {
        background-color: #5d5c61;
        transform: scale(1.1);
      }

      section {
        margin: 20px;
        padding: 20px;
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, #557a95, #7395ae);
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        opacity: 0;
        animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out forwards;
      }

      @keyframes fadeIn {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
        }
        to {
          opacity: 1;
        }
      }


      
      .container {
        min-height: 100vh;
        overflow: auto;
      }

      .about-content {
        text-align: justify;
        color: #fff;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .site-name {
        font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
        font-size: 2em;
        color: #74c2f6;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .btn-primary {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 8px 16px;
        background-color: #379683;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
      }

      .btn-primary:hover {
        background-color: #557a95;
        transform: scale(1.1);
      }
      a {
        color: #e8e8ee;
        font-family: "Trebuchet MS", "Lucida Sans Unicode", "Lucida Grande",
          "Lucida Sans", Arial, sans-serif;
      }
      a:hover {
        color: #74c2f6;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <header>
        <div class="site-name">Movies Hub</div>
      </header>

      <nav class="px-5">
        <a href="/home">Home</a>
        <a href="/movies">Movies</a>
        <a href="/watchlist">Watch List</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <button onclick="logout()" class="logout-btn">Logout</button>
      </nav>

      <section>
        <div class="about-content">
          <h2>About Movies Hub</h2>
          <p>
            Welcome to Movies Hub, your go-to place for discovering and enjoying
            a wide range of movies. Our platform offers a diverse collection of
            films, from classic masterpieces to the latest blockbusters.
          </p>
          <p>
            At Movies Hub, we are passionate about providing an immersive
            movie-watching experience. Whether you're a cinephile looking for
            hidden gems or someone seeking the latest releases, we've got you
            covered.
          </p>
          <p>
            Explore our carefully curated selection, create your watchlist, and
            enjoy the magic of cinema from the comfort of your home. Join our
            community of movie enthusiasts, and let the journey through the
            world of film begin!
          </p>
          <p>
            Movies Hub is dedicated to bringing you the best in entertainment.
            Our team of movie enthusiasts works tirelessly to ensure that you
            have access to a diverse and exciting array of films. From drama to
            action, comedy to romance, we've got something for everyone.
          </p>
          <p>
            Stay tuned for regular updates, featured playlists, and exclusive
            content. Dive into the world of Movies Hub and make every movie
            night a memorable experience. Thank you for being a part of our
            cinematic journey!
          </p>

          <h4>Requeted Movies</h4>
          <% for (let i = 0; i < num; i++) { %>
          <a href="/home"><%= movies[i].name %><span>.</span></a
          ><br />
          <% } %>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <script>
      function logout() {
        window.location.href = "/logout";
      }
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
